  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_llm-raw-scihub-o.O-ceat.200600266.pdf_2_7",
    "text": "The polypropylene hollow fibrous membrane assembly was purchased from Zheda Kaihua Technical Co. Ltd. The inner and outer diameters of the membrane are 0.32 and 0.47 mm, respectively. The area of the membrane assembly was 4 m?. The length and height of the membrane were 24 cm and 22.5 cm, respectively.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.07161943377193658,
      0.4912790696325939,
      0.4554263601201271,
