    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_llm-raw-scihub-o.O-ceat.200600266.pdf_2_42",
    "text": "The membrane flux in Fig. 2, curve (a) becomes stable after a transit reduction with an increase of operation time under 20 V/cm appending steady electric field strength. Its average membrane flux was the highest of all experiments carried out.",
